{"tid":718864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"直立滑浪失蹤男屍浮梅窩","createTime":"2018-06-27T04:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T05:42:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"701a0d36426303b2e435ce5bf1aaf130b251cbff","tid":718864,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:25:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180627/20432618\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180627%2F20432618&d=zM35jLS05zISECKmFrxpgDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=153f4b5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180627%2F20432618&h=868e5dfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180627/20432618</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月27日 <br />\n<br />\n直立滑浪失蹤男屍浮梅窩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180627/large/27la7p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180627%2Flarge%2F27la7p11.jpg&h=cd4f6682&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■消防前日派出蛙人於梅窩碼頭搜索失蹤男子。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】喜靈洲以東的周公島海面，昨天中午有人報稱發現一具人形物體載浮載沉，水警及消防輪到場撈起一具浮屍。警方調查後，證實浮屍身份為前天下午於梅窩碼頭對開，玩直立式滑浪板時墮海失蹤的49歲男子。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n水警撈起送到碼頭<br />\n<br />\n昨中午12時許，有市民於梅窩以東約五公里的周公島海面，發現一具人形物體漂浮海面，於是報警。水警及消防輪接報到場，將一名男子屍體撈起，然後送到梅窩碼頭。人員以毛氈覆蓋遺體，他身體已經發白。警方經調查後，證實浮屍是日前玩直立式滑浪板時墮海失蹤的49歲男子。<br />\n<br />\n前日中午，一名梅窩原居民中年男子，於梅窩碼頭對開海面約50米玩直立式滑浪板時，疑失平衡墮海沒頂失蹤，有人其後於銀礦灣發現失蹤男子的滑浪板。水警、消防輪及政府飛行服務直升機到場通宵搜索但無發現。<br />\n<br />\n■記者李晟謙  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n2014年起　貨車登記須有倒車cam<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n好教師生前愛帶學生行山"},{"pid":"639473714e350c6b07c62286aece8f1d16c99e03","tid":718864,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:29:56.000Z","msg":"49歲都唔化嘅"},{"pid":"649e52624f5dfec3f4f0ca674e9b6e8c13b95673","tid":718864,"uid":191450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:46:06.000Z","msg":"為興趣而死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79beae737d67ca856d69f4d2551ad231ac561393","tid":718864,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"649e52624f5dfec3f4f0ca674e9b6e8c13b95673","tid":718864,"uid":191450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:46:06.000Z","msg":"為興趣而死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:49:25.000Z","msg":"無悔！！"},{"pid":"73b9fd00f6488e87779c5ed81944d31b949a3189","tid":718864,"uid":116896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:10:30.000Z","msg":"教練 我想直立滑浪<br />\n老頭子，你最光輝的時刻是什麼，而我就是現在"},{"pid":"5d701a8cd777c10e7cd1c5b239d31938a0353c38","tid":718864,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:19:23.000Z","msg":"快樂到死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef746e80d5f630cd826a895fbf24f54239837b6","tid":718864,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:34:28.000Z","msg":"搏盡無悔"},{"pid":"ad55e8dba30df7faf24a5ba6462beaf4c7321a17","tid":718864,"uid":126046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:42:47.000Z","msg":"滑浪 唔係企係塊滑浪板度 仲有咩玩法？"}]}